✨ Al-Quddus (ٱلْقُدُّوسُ) – The Most Pure, The Most Holy ✨

📖 Ma’ni:
🔹 Al-Quddus ka matlab hai sab se paak, muqaddas, jo har qisam ke nuqs, kamzori aur aib se paak ho.
🔹 Allah Ta’ala ki zaat aur sifaat mein kisi qisam ki kami ya nuqs ka tasawwur bhi nahi.

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌿 Asal Lafz (Root): Qaf–Dal–Seen (ق د س)
➡️ Paak, saaf, be-aib
➡️ Har na-paaki se door
➡️ Muqaddas aur paakiza

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

📖 Qur’an mein zikr:
1️⃣ “Huwallahu la ilaha illa huwa Al-Malikul Quddus…” (59:23)
2️⃣ “Yusabbihu lillahi ma fis-samawati wama fil-ard Al-Malikil Quddusil-‘Azeezil-Hakeem” (62:1)

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🤲 Ahadith mein zikr:
✅ Nabi ﷺ sajda mein dua padhte: “Subbuhun Quddusun Rabbul-mala’ikati war-ruh” (Muslim 487a)
✅ Witr ke baad aap ﷺ kehte: “Subhanal-Malikil-Quddus” (3 martaba).

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🕊 Ruh al-Quddus (Holy Spirit):
📌 Qur’an mein kai martaba zikr aaya hai.
📌 Ulama ke mutabiq iska matlab Hazrat Jibreel (AS) hai,
   jo paighambaron ki Allah ke hukm se madad karte the, khaas taur par Hazrat ‘Isa (AS).

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________  

💡 Asar (Reflection):
✨ Allah sab buraiyon se paak hai.
✨ Humein bhi zahiri (cleanliness) aur batini (dil aur amal) dono taur par paak rehna chahiye.
✨ Gunahon aur buri aadaton se door rehkar qalb ko saaf rakhna chahiye.
✨ Tawbah aur istighfar se rooh paak ho jati hai.

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌸 Amal:
🔑 “Ya Quddus” ka wazifa dil ko paak aur niyyat ko khalis banata hai.
🔑 Har subah-shaam iska zikr roohani sukoon deta hai.

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌺 Short Reminder:
Al-Quddus matlab: Allah har nuqs, aib aur kami se paak hai.
👉 Humein apne a’maal aur dil ko bhi paak banane ki koshish karni chahiye.


